@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC" as ATCC
participant ":System" as System

activate ATCC
ATCC -> System : getScheduledFlightsByAircraft(aircraftRegistration)
activate System

note right of System: The system retrieves all scheduled\nflights assigned to the specified aircraft.

System --> ATCC : returns list of scheduled flights for the aircraft
deactivate System
deactivate ATCC
@enduml
